node.text: best modular Christmas tree ever

I had the privilege of producing a track on this record. It was a very moving experience, a big thank you to Leonard and Adam Cohen. The best part was to sit with Leonard's voice all by itself on solo to be honest it needed no music. I just did my best to do the lyrics justice. The song is called The Hills.

I just want to congratulate my most favourite person in the whole world, Heather O'Neill, for winning the Writers' Trust Fellowship award tonight!
I can't tell you how proud and lucky I am to be her boyfriend. Her books are absolutely amazing. It is such a privilege to share my life with such an overwhelmingly brilliant woman.
